    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Pitting all of your strength and resolve against your enemy, you deliver a strike that is impossible to ignore.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Vital Strike, base attack bonus +9.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever you use Vital Strike, Improved Vital Strike, or Greater Vital Strike, you gain a +2 bonus on each extra weapon damage dice roll those feats grant (+6 maximum). This bonus damage is multiplied on a critical hit.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>Whenever you use Vital Strike, Improved Vital Strike, or Greater Vital Strike, you can spend 5 stamina points to increase the bonus damage to +4 on each extra weapon damage die. For weapons with more than one damage die, count all of the weapon's base damage dice together as one set.",
